Regling Expects All Euro Region Governments to Back EFSF Boost

-- B y   P a t r i c k   D o n a h u e
-- 
2011-09-19T11:04:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/regling-expects-all-euro-region-governments-to-back-efsf-boost.html
Klaus Regling, head of the European
Financial Stability Facility, said he expects all euro area
members to vote for treaty changes on upgrading the European
bailout fund.   “I expect the changes to go through,” Regling told budget
committee lawmakers in  Germany ’s lower house of parliament today
in Berlin. He was asked whether the government in Slovakia would
vote for the changes.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Patrick Donahue at 
 pdonahue1@bloomberg.net  